<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期二早上，卢克和卡洛斯站在四年级教室的外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直在想。” 卡洛斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果我们现在和凯蒂和好，她会让我们跳方块舞的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克挑起眉毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等她发表完，我们再和她和好怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错。” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃哦！” 卢克说，“她过来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂沿着走廊大步走来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊拿着友谊测定仪跟在后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“朋友们！” 凯蒂喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们被抓住了，就像捕鼠器上的老鼠。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来跟你们说对不起。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了一眼乔伊，乔伊点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我错过了练习，对不起。我应该看时间的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卡洛斯？” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯低头看着脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，我不该发脾气。” 他小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卢克？” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克叹了口气。“我不该挂你的电话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊看着友谊测定仪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>指针指着笑脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好，可以了。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看来现在你们已经和好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克和卡洛斯什么也没说，他们跑进了教室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还不错，” 凯蒂说，“我觉得好多了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是吧？” 乔伊很开心，“友谊对你的健康有好处！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天下午，奥利维亚也发表了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿着一张海报，上面有个太阳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家觉得被太阳晒黑的皮肤很好看。” 奥利维亚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但过度的晒太阳会引起灼伤，甚至会导致皮肤癌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，请使用防晒霜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚拿起另一张海报。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在夏威夷，有一种虫子叫蜈蚣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们能长到三十厘米，还会刺人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这只黑虫子不是蜈蚣，是蜱虫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂咧嘴笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你路过一片高草地，” 奥利维亚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“进屋时，请确认有没有蜱虫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚拿起最后一张海报。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毒藤。” 她说，“如果你看见这样的植物，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有三片叶子，请离它远点儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你碰了它，请马上用肥皂和水洗一洗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不要等，不然就晚了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，奥利维亚递给大家一瓶护手霜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“护手霜能保护你的皮肤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是用夏威夷果做的，就像我的项链一样！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家试一试吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的发表非常好。” 贝柔老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下一个是卡洛斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你没有耳朵。” 卡洛斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你就听不到警报声、 火车声，甚至龙卷风声。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们听不见你的声音！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以，你必须保护好耳朵。” 卡洛斯看着他的纸条，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“声音过大会伤害你的耳朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果别人能听见你耳机里的声音，那说明音乐声太大了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯又看了一眼他的纸条。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要把尖锐的东西放进耳朵里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>事实上，不要把任何东西放进耳朵里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我说完了。” 说完，他回到了座位上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的发表很棒。” 凯蒂小声说，“简单明了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克的 “健康饮食” 是今天最后一个发表，他在发零食！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“食物就好像是身体的燃料！” 卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有食物，我们就不能跑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打开一张大海报，把它固定到了白板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个食物金字塔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这些零食是我妈妈准备的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>包括了这个金字塔里所有的食物群。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水果、蔬菜、谷类，乳制品和坚果！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“脆皮派在哪儿？” 拉里问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我这儿有一个坏消息。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“脆皮派不在这个金字塔上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？” 同学们喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“脆皮派里的脂肪和糖太多了，我们不应该经常吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因此，妈妈总会在菜单上加上很多健康的食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吃吧！” 卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>同学们吃东西时，凯蒂悄悄地走到卢克和卡洛斯身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，你们俩！” 她咧嘴笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天晚上能练习方块舞吗？我明天发表！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>